data.description: Stunning Ardmore Crossing Gem in Shelbyville at 409 Vildana Way! Step into modern elegance with this 2021-built residence nestled in the coveted Ardmore Crossing neighborhood of Shelbyville. Boasting a contemporary design yet retaining a welcoming warmth, this expansive 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath beauty promises an unparalleled living experience. As you enter, the sunlit main level warmly invites you to a regal dining room and a cozy breakfast nook. The impeccable kitchen stands out, with a functional island, spacious pantry, chic black appliances, and gleaming granite countertops. Adjacent, a spacious great room provides the perfect ambiance for relaxation. The additional flex space on this level is versatile, ideal for a productive home office or a lively game room. The second floor is a haven for tranquility. Here, the primary suite exudes luxury with its en-suite bathroom, which features a double sink vanity, a spacious walk-in shower, and a generous walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms all feature roomy closets, ensuring storage will never be an issue. The convenience continues with the hall bath and laundry room strategically positioned on this level. Moreover, the loft area presents a fantastic space for additional living or entertainment. Venture down to the mostly finished walk-out basement, and your options multiply. An expansive living area, a full bathroom, and a versatile room await, ready to be transformed into an office, gym, extra bedroom, or any space that meets your lifestyle needs. Outdoors, an expansive deck oversees a meticulously designed patio, perfect for both quiet moments and grand gatherings. The added fire-pit ensures memories year-round. This home also backs up to trees creating more privacy. Location-wise, this gem is a stone's throw away from the heart of Shelbyville. Known for its rich history, vibrant community, and picturesque landscapes, Shelbyville offers an array of amenities. From charming boutiques, top-notch eateries, cultural events, to serene parks and recreation areas, there's always something to explore. Plus, with the expressway just minutes away, accessibility and convenience are at your doorstep. In essence, this home is not just a residence but a lifestyle. Come, experience the blend of luxury, comfort, and the best of Shelbyville living at 409 Vildana Way!
